title: Jimi Hendrix - Kick Ass Live Vol.3r1: Are You Experienced? (JPIO
description:
Jimi Hendrix - Kick Ass Live Vol.3r1: Are You Experienced? (JPIO 029r1 / 29.08.2017 / 1CDR) 


(Compilation Live recordings of "Are You Experienced": State Fair Music Hall, Dallas, TX 16.02.68 (4) / Auditorium Theatre, Chicago, IL 10.08.68; 2nd Show (19) / Coliseum Ballroom, Davenport, IA 11.08.68 (5) / Merriweather Post Pavilion, Columbia, MD 16.08.68 (6) / New York Rock Festival, Singer Bowl, Flushing Meadows Park, Queens, New York City, NY 23.08.68 (7) / Memorial Coliseum, Phoenix, AZ 04.09.68 (8) / Memorial Coliseum, Portland, OR 09.09.68 (17) / Hollywood Bowl, Hollywood, CA 14.09.68 (9) / Winterland Ballroom, San Francisco, CA 10.10.68; 1st Show (10) / Winterland Ballroom, San Francisco, CA 11.10.68; 1st Show / Minneapolis Auditorium, Minneapolis, MN 02.11.68 (13) / Musikhalle, Hamburg 11.01.69; 1st Show (14) / Stimmen der Welt, Großer Saal, Konzerthaus, Vienna 22.01.69; 2nd Show (15) / Newport '69 Pop Festival, San Fernando State College, Devonshire Downs, CA 20.06.69 (16)) Aud except Sbd: San Francisco, CA 10.10.68 & Newport '69 Pop Festival 20.06.69; Lowest possibele Gen - Some tracks Speed corrected & Digitally Restored, 1 track EQ'd & 2 tracks Edited (Early fade outs) 
notes: 
- The Original Artwork lists the 2nd version of (8) [Memorial Coliseum, Phoenix, AZ 04.09.68, Upgrade] as being from Cologne 13.01.69, but "Are You Experienced" wasn't played there. 
- The venue for the Davenport show was for many years erroneously identified as the Colonial Ballroom.
